'''凱爾·克里斯蒂安·漢崔克斯'''（{{lang-en|Kyle Christian Hendricks}}，{{bd|1989年|12月7日}}），綽號“教授”，目前為[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]][[芝加哥小熊|芝加哥小熊]]的先發投手。身高190公分，體重86公斤，為右投右打的球員。

== 早期棒球生涯 ==
漢崔克斯高中就讀於加州米申維耶霍的卡皮斯特拉諾山谷高中，在2008年的大聯盟選秀裡，在第39輪被[[洛杉磯天使|洛杉磯天使]]選中，但是他並未簽約，反而是選擇就讀達特茅斯學院。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mymlbdraft.com/2008/round39/|title=2008 MLB Draft Results Round 39|accessdate=2016-11-15|archive-date=2016-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161101004746/http://www.mymlbdraft.com/2008/round39|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ocvarsity.com/sports/strong-5345-information-lakers.html |title=Capo Valley pitcher Hendricks signs with Dartmouth | strong, information, lakers - Sports |publisher=OC Varsity |date=January 4, 2008 |accessdate=August 10, 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714115849/http://www.ocvarsity.com/sports/strong-5345-information-lakers.html |archivedate=2014年7月14日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ocregister.com/articles/hendricks-160162-kyle-dartmouth.html |title=Whicker column: Baseballs over golf balls for Capistrano Valley pitcher. Capistrano Valley's Kyle Hendricks was good at golf but passionate for baseball, and now his pitching is rewarding his efforts |first=Mark |last=Whicker |work=The Orange County Register |date=April 26, 2008 |accessdate=June 9, 2014 |archive-date=2017-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301051415/http://www.ocregister.com/articles/hendricks-160162-kyle-dartmouth.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>在他的大學棒球生涯裡，他投了62局，6勝3敗，防禦率2.47以及投出70次三振。<ref name=milb/>

== 職業棒球生涯 ==
=== 小聯盟時期 ===
在2011年的大聯盟選秀裡，漢崔克斯在第八輪被[[德克薩斯遊騎兵|德州遊騎兵]]選中。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://thedartmouth.com/2011/07/08/sports/Hendricks |title=Texas Rangers select pitcher Kyle Hendricks '12 in MLB draft |publisher=TheDartmouth.com |date=July 8, 2011 |accessdate=August 10, 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110908042325/http://thedartmouth.com/2011/07/08/sports/Hendricks |archive-date=2011-09-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 於是他加入短期1A西北聯盟的史伯坎印地安人隊，開始他的職棒生涯。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://rangersblog.dallasnews.com/2011/06/rangers-sign-incredibly-smart.html/ |title=Rangers sign incredibly smart baseball player | Dallas Morning News |publisher=Rangersblog.dallasnews.com |date=June 10, 2011 |accessdate=June 9, 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714125029/http://rangersblog.dallasnews.com/2011/06/rangers-sign-incredibly-smart.html/ |archivedate=2014年7月14日 }}</ref> 在2012交易大限日前，他和Christian Villanueva一起被交易到[[芝加哥小熊|芝加哥小熊]]。<ref>{{cite web |author=John Arguello |url=http://www.chicagonow.com/cubs-den/2013/05/sleeper-prospect-kyle-hendricks-opening-some-eyes/ |title=Sleeper prospect Kyle Hendricks opening some eyes | Cubs Den |publisher=Chicagonow.com |date= |accessdate=August 10, 2013 |archive-date=2016-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821162606/http://www.chicagonow.com/cubs-den/2013/05/sleeper-prospect-kyle-hendricks-opening-some-eyes/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 而他在2013年進入2A打球，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.knoxnews.com/news/2013/jun/25/ryan-dempster-trade-came-with-expectations-for/ |title=Ryan Dempster trade came with expectations for current Smokies pitcher Kyle Hendricks " Knoxville News Sentinel |publisher=Knoxnews.com |date= |accessdate=June 9, 2014 |archive-date=2013-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131204195726/http://www.knoxnews.com/news/2013/jun/25/ryan-dempster-trade-came-with-expectations-for/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在季中升上3A。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.csnchicago.com/cubs/cubs-pitching-prospect-kyle-hendricks-turning-heads |title=Cubs pitching prospect Kyle Hendricks turning heads |publisher=CSN Chicago |date= |accessdate=August 10, 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130810092936/http://www.csnchicago.com/cubs/cubs-pitching-prospect-kyle-hendricks-turning-heads |archivedate=2013年8月10日 }}</ref> 
他在2014年5月12至18日，獲選為3A太平洋岸聯盟單週最佳投手。<ref name=milb>{{cite web |last=Jackson |first=Josh |url=http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140122&content_id=66481588&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_milb |title=Hendricks balanced pro ball, Ivy League | MiLB.com News | The Official Site of Minor League Baseball |publisher=Milb.com |date=January 22, 2014 |accessdate=June 9, 2014 |archive-date=2016-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914212223/http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140122&content_id=66481588&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_milb |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

=== 大聯盟時期 ===
==== 2014年 ====
由於Jeff Samardzija和[[傑森·漢默|傑森·漢默]]在2014年7月14日同時被交易至[[奧克蘭運動家|奧克蘭運動家]]，因此漢崔克斯在7月10日首度在大聯盟投手丘上登板對決[[辛辛那提紅人|辛辛那提紅人]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://espn.go.com/blog/chicago/cubs/post/_/id/25604/dallas-beeler-kyle-hendricks-to-face-reds |title=Dallas Beeler, Kyle Hendricks to face Reds |publisher=ESPNChicago.com |date=July 7, 2014 |accessdate=July 10, 2014 |archive-date=2015-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150225225605/http://espn.go.com/blog/chicago/cubs/post/_/id/25604/dallas-beeler-kyle-hendricks-to-face-reds |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在7月22日，他在客場擊敗[[聖地牙哥教士|聖地牙哥教士]]拿下了他的大聯盟首勝。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://scores.espn.go.com/mlb/boxscore?gameId=340722116|title=San Diego Padres vs. Chicago Cubs - Box Score - July 22, 2014 - ESPN|publisher=ESPN.com|date=July 22, 2014|accessdate=April 18, 2015|archive-date=2014-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140818002523/http://scores.espn.go.com/mlb/boxscore?gameId=340722116|dead-url=no}}</ref> 該年他拿下了國聯8月最佳新人。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Misener|first1=Jacob|title=Soler, Valaika drive in two a piece as Cubs roll|url=http://cubbiescrib.com/2014/09/03/jorge-soler-chris-valaika-drive-two-apiece-cubs-roll/|website=cubbiescrib.com|publisher=SI.com|accessdate=September 4, 2014|archive-date=2014-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140909084021/http://cubbiescrib.com/2014/09/03/jorge-soler-chris-valaika-drive-two-apiece-cubs-roll/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 這個球季他繳出7勝2敗，防禦率2.46的成績單。<ref name="IndyStar">{{cite web | url=http://www.indystar.com/story/sports/baseball/2015/02/11/chicago-cubs-prospects-kris-bryant-jorge-soler/23238635/ | title=Cubs young talent ready to make imprint in majors | publisher=[[Indy_Star|Indy Star]] | author=Hendricks, Maggie | date=February 11, 2015 | accessdate=February 25, 2015 | archive-date=2018-08-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180804103159/https://www.indystar.com/story/sports/baseball/2015/02/11/chicago-cubs-prospects-kris-bryant-jorge-soler/23238635/ | dead-url=no }}</ref> <ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_2014.shtml#NLroy | title=NL Rookie of the Year Voting | publisher=[[Baseball_Reference|Baseball Reference]] | accessdate=2016-11-15 | archive-date=2016-11-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161119131518/http://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_2014.shtml#NLroy | dead-url=no }}</ref>

==== 2015年 ====
基於前一年的好表現，漢崔克斯在2015年開季前就進入了開季先發輪值。由[[喬恩·萊斯特|喬恩·萊斯特]]擔任一號先發，漢崔克斯擔任二號先發。<ref name="IndyStar" /><ref>{{cite web | url=http://chicago.suntimes.com/baseball/7/71/387661/year-turning-4-year-deal-cubs-wood-starts | publisher=[[Chicago_Sun_Times|Chicago Sun Times]] | date=February 22, 2015 | accessdate=February 25, 2015 | author=Wittenmyer, Gordon | title=Year after turning down 4-year deal from Cubs, Wood turns page | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150225125617/http://chicago.suntimes.com/baseball/7/71/387661/year-turning-4-year-deal-cubs-wood-starts | archive-date=2015-02-25 | dead-url=yes }}</ref> 在5月21號，漢崔克斯面對聖地牙哥教士時，投出生涯首場完封。在他整季180局的投球內容中，他的戰績8勝7敗，防禦率3.95。<ref>{{cite web|title=MLB Stats|url=http://m.mlb.com/player/543294/kyle-hendricks|website=m.mlb.com|publisher=MLB.com|accessdate=October 3, 2016|archive-date=2016-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161118220718/http://m.mlb.com/player/543294/kyle-hendricks|dead-url=no}}</ref> 他也分別在[[2015年國家聯盟分區賽|國聯分區賽]]和[[2015年國家聯盟冠軍賽|國聯冠軍賽]]的第二和第三場擔任先發。

==== 2016年 ====
在2016上半季，漢崔克斯投出7勝6敗，不過防禦率2.55是全隊最低。在5月28日面對[[費城費城人|費城費城人]]時，他再度投滿9局並且只失掉1分。8月1日，漢崔克斯又投出生涯第二場完封，當時球隊以5:0擊敗[[邁阿密馬林魚|邁阿密馬林魚]]，截至8月7日，漢崔克斯投出第17勝，防禦率也降至2.17，為大聯盟第二低。到了9月，他總共投了159局，13勝7敗，但防禦率僅2.09，使他成為大聯盟的防禦率王。<ref>{{cite web|title=Bryant named NL Player of the Month, Hendricks named NL Pitcher of the Month|url=http://wgntv.com/2016/09/03/bryant-named-nl-player-of-the-month-hendricks-named-nl-pitcher-of-the-month/|website=wgntv.com|publisher=WGN TV|accessdate=September 6, 2016|archive-date=2016-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160904160817/http://wgntv.com/2016/09/03/bryant-named-nl-player-of-the-month-hendricks-named-nl-pitcher-of-the-month/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 這季他16勝8敗，投了190局，防禦率僅2.13。這也是小熊隊自1938年以後，首度有投手成為大聯盟防禦率王。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Pace|first1=Cody|title=Hendricks ends regular season with ERA title|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/204713010/cubs-kyle-hendricks-earns-era-title/?game_pk=449284|website=m.mlb.com|publisher=MLB.com|accessdate=October 3, 2016|archive-date=2016-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005083349/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/204713010/cubs-kyle-hendricks-earns-era-title/?game_pk=449284|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在國聯冠軍賽第6場，漢崔克斯主投7又1/3局，只被敲出2安和投出1個保送，技壓道奇王牌[[克萊頓·克蕭|克萊頓·克蕭]]，使得小熊自1945後首度進軍[[2016年世界大賽|世界大賽]]，後來在世界大賽的第3和第7場先發，最後小熊獲得睽違108年的冠軍。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Bastian|first1=Jordan|last2=Muskat|first2=Carrie|title=Chicago Cubs win 2016 World Series|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/207938228/chicago-cubs-win-2016-world-series/|publisher=MLB|accessdate=November 3, 2016|archive-date=2017-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171130223630/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/207938228/chicago-cubs-win-2016-world-series/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==== 2017年 ====
6月8日，漢崔克斯因右手手指受傷而被放進10天傷兵名單。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Muskat|first1=Carrie|title=Kyle Hendricks goes on DL with finger injury|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/235211646/cubs-kyle-hendricks-lands-on-disabled-list/?topicId=27118122|publisher=MLB|accessdate=June 8, 2017}}</ref>最後他該季7勝5敗，防禦率3.03。季後賽，漢崔克斯在國聯分區賽的首戰及最終戰登板，還有國聯冠軍戰的第3戰。他總共主投17局，防禦率3.94，1勝1敗。最終小熊在國聯冠軍戰遭到道奇淘汰。

